With the exception of a few outliers (6800, 3500) this looks fairly well distributed and appears to correspond with the scope of the categories. The outlying categories in question are "Paedagogische Psychologie", "Wirtschaftkunde, Wirtschaftslehre" and "Politisch-gesellschaftlicher Unterricht, Politische Bildung", which sounds popular enough.

